<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Dear <%= @contract[:applicant][:first_name] %> <%= @contract[:applicant][:last_name] %>,</p>
    <p>
      You have yet to accept or reject your offer for the TAship of <%= @contract[:position] %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have not accept your offer by <%= @contract[:deadline] %>, your offer will be revoked. Until you have accepted the offer, we cannot pay you. If you plan to reject the offer, please do so promptly. If you have any questions, please contact the course instructor or the TA coordinator at tacoord@cs.toronto.edu. This is your <%= @contract[:nag_count] %><%= @contract[:nag_suffix] %> warning.
    </p>
    <p>
      Follow the link below to submit your final decision:<br/>
      <%= @url %>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
